window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Kabir, Amaira, Kushank and Suhani - four very different people bound together by love and friendship - struggling to find the motto of their lives. Four individuals striving to find themselves. Four threads entangled together and four lives recuperating each other. <i>No Matter What I Do</i> is the story of these four youngsters, on a journey to find themselves. </p> <p>The love story narrates tales of reversing stereotypes and finding individuality. But will they really find their reason to live? </p>"; 
